Initialize HumanPop Parameters for HumanPop

make a list of pars for HumanPop

HumanPop.Parameters(nSite, demographics = NULL, ...)

Arguments

nSite

number of sites (either FeedingSite or link{MacroPatch})
demographics

either a list or NULL; if NULL then sitePops is used to generate these parameters, see that function for details on the list structure that is expected.
...

additional named arguments for sitePops

Value

return a list HumanPop_PAR

Examples

HumanPop.Parameters(nSite = 5)
